OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FThe UK will announce a new set of
OL,7,Fsanctions on Russia as Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fsought to underline the government's
OL,9,Fcommitment to supporting Ukraine in
OL,10,Fits war against Moscow.
OL,12,FStarmer is among world leaders
OL,13,Fattending the G7 summit in Evian-les-
OL,14,FBains, France, with Ukraine, along
OL,15,Fwith the recently announced Iran peace
OL,16,Fdeal, at the top of the agenda.
OL,26,@uD@\rb
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
