CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781570085
OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FStarmer's announcement comes nearly a
OL,7,Fweek after his former defence
OL,8,Fsecretary John Healey and the minister
OL,9,Ffor armed forces quit, accusing the
OL,10,Fprime minister of failing to "commit
OL,11,Fthe resources that the nation needs to
OL,12,Fdefend the country".
OL,14,FFollowing Healy's resignation,
OL,15,FWashington urged the UK to bolster its
OL,16,Fmilitary strength with "urgency,
OL,17,Fscale, and determination".
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
