OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781570085
OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FDuring a roundtable at the summit,
OL,7,Fwhich will include US president Donald
OL,8,FTrump, Starmer is due to reiterate
OL,9,Fthat the fighting in Ukraine needs to
OL,10,Fstop.
OL,12,FNo 10 said Starmer had directed
OL,13,Fofficials in recent weeks to step up
OL,14,Fpressure on Moscow, including action
OL,15,Fon Russia's shadow fleet.
OL,17,FThe British armed forces intercepted a
OL,18,FRussian shadow fleet vessel in the
OL,19,FChannel in the early hours of Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
