PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781570085
OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) said
OL,7,FRoyal Marine commandos and specially
OL,8,Ftrained law enforcement officers from
OL,9,Fthe National Crime Agency boarded a
OL,10,Fsanctioned oil tanker during a six-
OL,11,Fhour operation ` the first UK-led
OL,12,Foperation of its kind.
OL,14,FIn a statement ahead of the
OL,15,Fannouncement, Starmer said: "Russia's
OL,16,Faggression threatens not just Ukraine,
OL,17,Fbut the security of all Europe.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781570085
OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,F"That is why the UK is stepping up `
OL,7,Fchoking off the revenues that fuel
OL,8,FPutin's war and powering Ukraine
OL,9,Fthrough the winters ahead.
OL,11,F"We will stand with Ukraine for as
OL,12,Flong as it takes and this announcement
OL,13,Freinforces that. Putin should roll
OL,14,Fback his tanks, end his barbaric
OL,15,Fstrikes, and come to the negotiating
OL,16,Ftable."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
