OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FLast week, Starmer hosted Ukrainian
OL,7,Fleader Volodymyr Zelenskyy along with
OL,8,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron and
OL,9,FGerman Chancellor Friedrich Merz `
OL,10,Fsome of Kyiv's staunchest allies ` at
OL,11,FNo 10 on Sunday evening for talks on
OL,12,Fthe war.
OL,14,FThe leaders called on Russian
OL,15,FPresident Vladimir Putin to agree "an
OL,16,Fimmediate and complete ceasefire" with
OL,17,Fthe current line of contact as a
OL,18,Fstarting point for any negotiations,
OL,19,FDowning Street said.
