OL,3,CUK to bolster support for Ukraine with
OL,4,Cswathe of sanctions against Russia
OL,6,FThe UK will give #210 million of UK
OL,7,FExport Finance support to enable UK-
OL,8,Fbased Urenco to supply enriched
OL,9,Furanium to Ukraine's nuclear power
OL,10,Fproducer, Energoatom, which provides
OL,11,Fmore than 50% of the country's
OL,12,Felectricity.
OL,14,FThe deal was agreed between the prime
OL,15,Fminister and Zelenskyy during their
OL,16,Fmeeting at Downing Street last week.
OL,18,FThe UK is expected to be among the
OL,19,Ffirst to impose sanctions on several
OL,20,FLiquefied Natural Gas (LNG) vessels
OL,21,Fmoving sanctioned Russian LNG.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
